                        document.getElementById("btnYiwen109401792098").style.display = "block";
                    </script>
</div>
<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_109401792098.aspx"><b>下武</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson109401792098">
<p>下武维周，世有哲王。三后在天，王配于京。</p>
<p>王配于京，世德作求。永言配命，成王之孚。</p>
<p>成王之孚，下土之式。永言孝思，孝思维则。</p>
<p>媚兹一人，应侯顺德。永言孝思，昭哉嗣服。</p>
<p>昭兹来许，绳其祖武。於万斯年，受天之祜。</p>
<p>受天之祜，四方来贺。於万斯年，不遐有佐。</p>
</div>
</div>
